	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64210446">Hmm, jetting droplets into air are not the same as sucking in 'solid' water.  With your typical roughly made Chinese sprinkler, it could indeed rotate in any direction when sucking in water, depending on manufactured flaws.</div>
	</div>

